title: Lamamra receives Jordanian Foreign Minister Ayman Safadi
text: Minister of Foreign Affairs and National Community Abroad Ramtane Lamamra held Saturday evening, in Algiers, talks with Jordanâ€™s Deputy Prime Minister and Minister of Foreign Affairs and Expatriates Ayman Al-Safadi on ways to promote the bilateral relations and the ongoing preparations for the holding of the next Arab Summit in Algiers.
